{"id": 1525, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x老板电器】说起来，为什么你在家吃饭越来越难了？", "description": "来跟我们聊聊，你那拥抱健康新生活的梦想都是如何遇到重重阻挠的。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7003, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170221122645Rxtu8OHASYJUDBPM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-22T03:00:10Z", "options": [{"id": 170241, "content": "厨艺不精", "image": "img/option/option/20170222233826wAmbIL4UvfhBDc5o", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889494}, {"id": 169986, "content": "因为穷，所以没时间做饭，又因为穷，所以在外吃不起饭。人生好多难题啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943737}, {"id": 170242, "content": "在外面吃饭叫果腹，在家做饭叫情调。情调哪会天天有（摊手", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480625}, {"id": 169987, "content": "其实烧一壶开水泡一碗燕麦再烫个青菜加一些调料，配个坚果或者市售酱牛肉，不用开火没有油烟真心也很好吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921463}, {"id": 170243, "content": "偶尔想做菜的时候会把它当成一种艺术，烹饪和摆盘都觉得很享受。但是前期的食材准备和后面的洗碗擦桌实在是累而且毫无趣味啊。说到底大概还是嫌麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922068}, {"id": 172035, "content": "懒，拖延", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208827}, {"id": 169988, "content": "做一顿好吃的饭要花很多心思啊，一个人太麻烦Ծ‸Ծ", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944047}, {"id": 169989, "content": "我妈的黑暗料理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603974}, {"id": 170245, "content": "6点以后下班挤完地铁饿得只想立刻在家门口打包一份套餐接着窝在沙发上边吃边撸剧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759724}, {"id": 169990, "content": "一直在外面念书 习惯了食堂风格和外卖风格 有时家里做一桌子菜不习惯也不符合我的食物习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935091}, {"id": 170246, "content": "买菜洗菜切菜炒菜，做饭时间超过一个半小时，二十分钟吃完，再加刷碗，这个帐要怎么算？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266767}, {"id": 169991, "content": "最近准备买房，还是自己带省钱（叹气）不过也发现自己吃惯了家里饭就不太想出去吃香喝辣了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943918}, {"id": 170247, "content": "我在家做饭，因为外面吃太贵了，哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945566}, {"id": 169992, "content": "觉得麻烦，懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943045}, {"id": 171016, "content": "仅仅因为我懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943391}, {"id": 170249, "content": "思考明天的菜谱简直就是折磨，家里人这个不爱吃那个，那个不想吃这个，还得每天比重样，还不如下馆子吃……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213632}, {"id": 169994, "content": "不想洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760554}, {"id": 169995, "content": "因为外面好吃的是真的多~", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942273}, {"id": 170251, "content": "因为洗碗麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840753}, {"id": 169996, "content": "怕油烟，怕麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912650}, {"id": 169997, "content": "不会做，也并不想学←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942920}, {"id": 170253, "content": "我想给我对象天天做饭，可是我没有?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908034}, {"id": 169998, "content": "不会做，也并不想学←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942920}, {"id": 170254, "content": "手机不好玩吗 如此宝贵的时间为什么要用在做饭上", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945593}, {"id": 171278, "content": "我做饭得有人洗碗啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126700}, {"id": 169999, "content": "不会做，也并不想学←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942920}, {"id": 170255, "content": "油烟过敏", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 170000, "content": "不会做，也并不想学←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942920}, {"id": 170001, "content": "没时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797404}, {"id": 170257, "content": "钱少事多离家远", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717805}, {"id": 170769, "content": "不想洗碗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900075}, {"id": 170002, "content": "在家做一人食倒是不难，就是食材不好买，买多了吃不完，买少了显得单调", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926262}, {"id": 173586, "content": "不仅单身狗，而且懒！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954825}, {"id": 170515, "content": "经常自己做一个人的晚餐，相比外卖觉得自己做的更卫生也吃的更放心…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911228}, {"id": 170260, "content": "没成家呗，成家就在家吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938921}, {"id": 170772, "content": "食堂解决了我的一日三餐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927523}, {"id": 170005, "content": "下班太晚，且，一个人~", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907558}, {"id": 170006, "content": "一两小时做饭，再花半小时刷碗刷锅，然而吃饭只是10分钟，还是把生命浪费在更有点意义的事情上吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663461}, {"id": 170008, "content": "时间少人少和懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904862}, {"id": 170264, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943147}, {"id": 170010, "content": "在哪吃都一样，外面吃主要为了省事", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344467}, {"id": 170011, "content": "主要是刷碗很麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601802}, {"id": 171804, "content": "怕麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941086}, {"id": 170013, "content": "一顿好饭吃三天?", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944805}, {"id": 170014, "content": "外卖越来越方便了呀。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909974}, {"id": 171038, "content": "因为外面不用洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947325}, {"id": 170015, "content": "单身是原罪。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130873}, {"id": 170016, "content": "加班直接过饭点，回家到半夜也没有做饭的时间。至于周末。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742602}, {"id": 170272, "content": "因为肥 一个人做饭 肯定吃不完 吃完了又撑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205349}, {"id": 171040, "content": "不会做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945483}]}